description: Starts a new session for an Amazon Q App, allowing inputs to be provided and the app to be run.

parameters.name: instanceId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Amazon Q Business application environment instance.

parameters.name: appId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Q App to start a session for.

parameters.name: appVersion
parameters.description: The version of the Q App to use for the session.

parameters.name: initialValues
parameters.description: Optional initial input values to provide for the Q App session. (dict) --- The value or result associated with a card in a Amazon Q App session. The unique identifier of the card. The value or result associated with the card. submissionMutation (dict) --- The structure that describes how the current form card value is mutated. Only applies for form cards when multiple responses are allowed. The unique identifier of the submission. The operation that is performed on a submission.

nested_params.name: cardId
nested_params.description: The unique identifier of the card.

nested_params.name: value
nested_params.description: The value or result associated with the card.

nested_params.name: submissionMutation
nested_params.description: The structure that describes how the current form card value is mutated. Only applies for form cards when multiple responses are allowed.

nested_params.name: submissionId
nested_params.description: The unique identifier of the submission.

nested_params.name: mutationType
nested_params.description: The operation that is performed on a submission.

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: Optional tags to associate with the new Q App session. (string) --- (string) ---

nested_items.name: sessionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the new or retrieved Q App session.

nested_items.name: sessionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the new Q App session.
